SmartThings,is,a,platform,that,allows,users,to,control,physical,things,such,as,locks,and,lights,with,their,smartphone,SmartThings,makes,it,possible,to,control,multiple,devices,and,things,with,one,application,The,SmartThings,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,SmartThings,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,setting,reminders,turning,things,off,and,on,and,managing,devices,and,things